Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Restore Classic Right-Click Context Menu (Windows 11)
; Author: C-Man | Date: 2026-02-28
;
; Windows 11 uses a simplified context menu by default.
; This restores the full classic context menu.
;
; To undo: delete the key below or run the companion undo reg file.
; A restart or explorer restart is required after applying.

[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Classes\CLSID\{86ca1aa0-34aa-4e8b-a509-50c905bae2a2}\InprocServer32]
@=""
